535
00:27:10,220 --> 00:27:11,100
Okay.

536
00:27:11,850 --> 00:27:12,790
Have you eaten?

537
00:27:13,090 --> 00:27:13,640
Yes, I have.

538
00:27:16,440 --> 00:27:18,020
I'm a bit tired.

539
00:27:18,360 --> 00:27:19,610
