544
00:27:29,520 --> 00:27:30,220
Okay.

545
00:27:38,440 --> 00:27:40,480
If you don't want to study,

546
00:27:40,510 --> 00:27:41,980
then go learn to cook.

547
00:27:43,670 --> 00:27:45,570
As long as it makes you happy,

548
00:27:46,220 --> 00:27:47,330
I'll support you.

549
00:27:49,900 --> 00:27:51,690
Before the economic reform,

550
00:27:51,730 --> 00:27:53,770
chefs were looked down upon.

551
00:27:54,390 --> 00:27:56,140
It's not like that anymore.

552
00:27:56,960 --> 00:27:58,040
Cooking is

553
00:27:58,310 --> 00:27:59,380
a form of artistry too.

554
00:27:59,720 --> 00:28:00,280
That's right.

555
00:28:00,300 --> 00:28:03,420
A good chef is an artist.

556
00:28:03,850 --> 00:28:06,530
With exceptional skills,

557
00:28:06,550 --> 00:28:07,860
you can conquer the world.

558
00:28:10,410 --> 00:28:12,930
Master one skill, and it’ll take you far.

559
00:28:23,710 --> 00:28:25,030
You said you wanted to take a nap.

560
00:28:27,680 --> 00:28:28,540
You forgot?

