00:28:47,990 --> 00:28:48,710
Granny Ma!

563
00:28:52,980 --> 00:28:54,160
Granny Ma!

564
00:28:55,240 --> 00:28:56,430
It's me, Zhou.

565
00:28:59,030 --> 00:29:00,310
Granny Ma!

566
00:29:00,660 --> 00:29:02,660
-Mr. Zhou! Mr. Zhou!
-Mr. Zhou!

567
00:29:02,690 --> 00:29:04,130
What are you doing?

568
00:29:04,570 --> 00:29:05,850
I haven't seen

569
00:29:06,090 --> 00:29:07,290
Granny Ma all day.

570
00:29:07,680 --> 00:29:09,440
